programme.title: Aku Raja Lawak

programme.title: Bayangan Emilia

programme.title: Gebu Gebu Manis

programme.title: Wartawan Kampung

Akhirnya, berita menjadi finah, kampung pula menjadi porak-poranda.

programme.title: Perempuan Disarung Ungu

programme.title: Meniti Cinta Di Starimost

Mummy makes mealtime more fun by pretending to be different animals. The family has a picnic and helps some ants collect crumbs and Mia and Max enjoy a bike ride with their friend Tootson the Train.

programme.title: Blippi Wonders
programme.desc: Lets love our planet with Blippi and friends! In a special musical episode, they sing all about recycling and taking care of the Earth. Blippi and Meekah build the ultimate playground, the Blippi Clubhouse! Then, join an adventure down a river as a boulder becomes sand and travel back in time to see how even the smallest dinosaur can be a big help. Blippi also learns about lions and how to mix colors to paint a beautiful rainbow.

programme.title: Blippi Wonders
programme.desc: Get ready for some thrilling adventures with Blippi Wonders! This journey is packed with excitement and learning. Discover how a firetruck and a police car work, learn about the sticky science of glue, and see the amazing power of magnets. Its a fun-filled exploration of the amazing things that make our world work.

programme.title: Go Buster
programme.desc: Buster has a wobbly tooth and its the start of a big adventure! After getting hit by a football, he and his friends race to the dentist. He and his friends get stuck in the mud on their way to see shooting stars and get lost in a storm in the woods. Buster also gets a surprise paint job, becomes a flying superhero and discovers a monster in the frightful forest.

programme.title: Go Buster
programme.desc: Learn how to stay clean and healthy with Buster! When Buster gets stuck in the mud and then a slimy green puddle, he needs to go to the carwash to get clean. After getting a wobbly tooth from eating too many sweets, he learns about the importance of good dental hygiene. Plus, see what happens when Buster gets sick and his friend Scout fetches Amber the Ambulance to help him feel better.

programme.title: CoComelon
programme.desc: Its song and dance time! Join JJ, his friends and family celebrating lifes big moments for little kids. Come along and be part of their fun everyday adventures.

programme.title: CoComelon
programme.desc: Lets learn about teeth and food! Join JJ to discover his favorite pizza toppings and then take a trip to a farm to count apples. After all that yummy food, learn how to take care of your teeth by brushing them well. When JJ gets nervous about a dentist visit, his siblings show him it can be fun. Plus, learn how to make a healthy and delicious frozen fruit treat!

programme.title: CoComelon
programme.desc: Its time for some fun with friends! In this playful story, JJ and his best pals learn how to share their toys and work together as a team. From the playground to the classroom, they discover that every activity is more fun when you do it with friends. Its a musical celebration of teamwork and friendship.

programme.title: CoComelon Classroom
programme.desc: Join Ms. Appleberry and JJ for a learning adventure! Explore the letters B, C, R and U through fun activities. Play pretend as you make beep-beep sounds on a bus and act like a playful pup. Sing along to classic songs, discover surprises inside the Melon Learning Box with a special guest and enjoy a rainy day adventure.

programme.title: Geckos Garage
programme.desc: Baby Truck is always ready for an adventure, and today hes leading his friends on an exciting exploration! Their playtime takes a messy turn when Baby Trucks curiosity gets the better of him, and he ends up stuck deep in the mud. It looks like hes in real trouble, but his friends wont leave him behind. This is a wonderful tale of how the smallest heroes, working together as a team, can solve even the stickiest of problems.

programme.title: Geckos Garage
programme.desc: Theres always something exciting happening at Geckos Garage! Today, a cement mixer has made a big mess, and a monster truck has a flat tire. Gecko must use all his tools and skills to help his vehicle friends get back on the road. Its a story about problem-solving and the joy of helping others.

programme.title: Rob the Robot
programme.desc: The crew gets tricked when Robs magic show goes wrong and Squeak is accidentally turned into a bunny! The friends must travel to the Magic Planet to find a way to change him back. After that magical mishap, the gang celebrates Imagination Day by traveling to a planet where they can each act out being their favorite imaginary character.

programme.title: Rob the Robot
programme.desc: Its a sure sign of a new mission when TK receives a message she cant understand. They travel to the Language Planet for help, only to find the robot in charge cant speak or hear. After solving that riddle, Squeak gets hungry and the crew travels to the Cheese Planet to find him the best snack ever.

programme.title: CoComelon

Its a day of happy songs and playful learning!

Dance with the animals in the jungle and see all the different vehicles on the street. End the day with a fun pajama dance party to get all the wiggles out before bed.

programme.title: CoComelon
programme.desc: Join JJ for a fantastic sing-along! Learn how to make all kinds of pasta with Grandma. Visit the new petting zoo at the farm and meet all the adorable baby animals. After a fun day, learn why its important to clean up. Give Bingo a bath to get him sparkly clean and then have a surprise picnic for Mom and Dad. Its a day full of fantastic fun and songs!

programme.title: ARPO
programme.desc: Prepare for pandemonium! Arpo and Daniels attempt at gardening takes a dangerous turn when their plant grows into a monstrous creature that tries to eat everyone. As if thats not enough, the new smart house system goes haywire, and the furniture starts a rebellion. Its up to Arpo to fix the pandemonium in this action-packed adventure.

programme.title: ARPO
programme.desc: With his new teaching chip, Arpo is on a mission to educate Daniel about the world around him. Together, they learn crucial safety skills, like what to do during an earthquake or a fire. Their lessons also venture into the realm of science, as they explore the power of magnets, the mystery of electricity, and even what to do when a scary monster appears! This is an educational and exciting journey where safety and science become a fun-filled playtime.

programme.title: Morphle
programme.desc: Mila and Morphle are having a day focused on helping little ones, but their plans are thrown into chaos by one baby-sized problem after another! First, they have to spring into action to save a friends baby carriage when it starts rolling away. Soon after, they discover a group of adorable but naughty baby Morphles running wild through the city, forcing them to find a way to round them all up safely.

programme.title: Morphle
programme.desc: A strange magic is bringing objects to life all over Petport, and Jordie is the first to notice when his bed sprouts legs and runs away! While chasing it, Mila and Morphle discover the problem is bigger than they thought, as they must also wrangle a magic carpet on a wild flight. Their adventure is a frantic chase to catch and calm the enchanted items causing chaos across the city.

programme.title: Cute Pet Guide
programme.desc: The era of high housing prices shocks the masses. However, some are willing to live in the mountains for their beloved parrots, just to give them the best breeding environment. Parrots have a long lifespan and their IQ is comparable to that of a five-year-old child. How do you make them behave? Training is actually a good way, but how? "Melon seeds" are key to the goal. programme.title: Scruffts
programme.desc: Six dogs, six handlers, all competing in the worlds largest and most famous dog show: "Crufts".nnBut they are not the pedigree pooches who compete to be labelled "Best in Show". These are the loveable family pets competing to win the "Scruffts" title.

programme.title: Cute Pets At Home
programme.desc: The Japanese animated film My Neighbor Totoro, which is popular all over the world is the childhood memory of many. Totoros classic furry body, round eyes and cute expression are very endearing. In South America, there is a kind of chinchilla that looks very similar to Totoro in the film. I heard that Taiwan now allows legal imports of these animals for breeding! Today, lets follow the Totoro zoo owner Molly and fall in love with the soft and cute charm of this animation star!

programme.title: Cute Pets At Home
programme.desc: Sulcata tortoises are the third largest land tortoise in the world, native to the Sahel Corridor in Africa. They do not come from the desert!!! They need to take baths and drink water too!!!nThey are 5 to 7 centimeters tall at birth, with bright black eyes that are super attractive. They grow really fast when healthy, adults can reach 0.9 meters in size and live over 100 years. But they will easily catch a cold and get sick if you are not careful. How to keep your turtles healthy? Lets hear what the experts say!

programme.title: Zoo Vet At Large
programme.desc: An orphaned badger cub puts up a fight when Dr. Matt gets him on the operating table. At Flamingoland, alls not well with a baby giraffe rejected by his mother at birth. programme.title: Cute Pet Guide
programme.desc: The meerkat king from "Madagascar" is funny, but meerkats in real life are well-behaved, cuddly and they heal our hearts! programme.title: Jerkin and GRILLIN
programme.desc: Back from a trip to Negril, Jamaica, chef Derrell Smith brings his favorite dishes back to his own yard! Grillin up Jerk Chicken, Saltfish and Ackee, coconut peas and rice and other Caribbean favorites for his two friends.

programme.title: Happy Birthday to Me
programme.desc: Chef Derrell Smiths birthday and hes treating himself to some self love and a lavish steak dinner inspired by a famous NYC steakhouse. On the menu: Rib Eye Steak with Peppercorn Sauce, Duck Frites, Wedge Salad and a celebratory carrot cake.

programme.title: Brunch Grows Up
programme.desc: Enough with the endless lines and mimosas! Chef Derrell Smith has leveled up his brunch by hosting his own. Todays menu, a "yelluh" grit bowl bar with toppings; Beer Braised Pulled Pork, Chili Fried Eggs, Bang Bang Shrimp and Tajin-rimmed Palomas.

programme.title: Grandma Estelle
programme.desc: Chef Derrell Smiths grandma inspired him in life and in the kitchen. He shares family recipes taking him right back to grandmas table. Hes cookin up Fried Chicken, Mac N Cheese, Collard Green Slaw, Brlee Banana Pudding and Pop-pops moonshine.

programme.title: Farmers Market Finds
programme.desc: Chef Derrell Smith heads to the Farmers Market for the first time. Inspired by rows of fresh fruit, veggies and the local farmers he creates a flavorful meal like Veggie Focaccia, Mushroom Medley Pasta, Spiced Apple Cobbler and a crisp white Sangria.

programme.title: A South Carolina Family Reunion
programme.desc: For his reunion inspired menu Chef Derrell Smith is going back to his roots. Cookin up some modern takes on the family classics including his Garlic Pesto Potato Salad, Salmon Filet, a Herby, Spicy Kale Slaw, and Grilled Fruit Skewers.

programme.title: Pre-Gaming!
programme.desc: As a former NFL player, game days hit a little different. These days chef Derrell Smith isnt on the field, hes changing the game in the kitchen with eats like Philly Cheesesteak Taquitos, Oyster Mushroom Wings and Elote Queso with Chili Lime Chips.

programme.title: Dinner Party
programme.desc: Chef Derrell Smith is hosting a dinner party! Living in KoreaTown, Derrell has fallen in love with its food and culture. Tonight, hes servin up Braised Beef Short Rib with Crispy Rice Cakes, Pickled Cabbage, Glass Noodles Salad and Korean Pancakes.

programme.title: Pierogies, Bagels, and Ramen in NYC
programme.desc: Frankie Celenza takes a LOT of bites out of the big apple as he samples warm pillowy bagels And schmear, grabs pierogies at an old school Ukrainian spot, gets the scoop on innovative ice cream flavors, and slurps up some real ramen.

programme.title: Tacos, Brats, And Biscuits in Austin
programme.desc: Frankie Celenza goes down south to try Austins best bets - breakfast tacos are on the itinerary, as well as a bangin beer garden And sausage house, loaded biscuits, and dessert pancakes to boot! Austin may be weird but the food is fabulous.

programme.title: Smash Burgers And A Slice in Los Angeles
programme.desc: Frankie Celenza heads to all the buzzworthy spots in LA - cooking up calamari steak at a classic Mexican joint, tasting taro root donuts with fun flavors, grabbing a guanciale slice, and hopping on the line to make cheesy scrumptious smash burgers.

programme.title: La Trepadora - S01:E112
programme.desc: Una gran sorpresa se lleva Victoria cuando el secuestrador le afirma que Nicols Del Casal intenta rescatarla; un furioso Sergio trata de convencer a Victoria de no creer en la informacion del delincuente. Convencido de rescatar a Victoria, Nicols ha preparado un plan para salvar a Victoria si no se hace efectivo el rescate, y as se lo manifiesta a Felipe. Ante la llegada de Hilario y Moncho a Cantarrana, Adelaida pregunta por su hija y teme lo peor, pues no se pudo efectuar el rescate. Cuando el otro hombre que vigilaba a Victoria decide ir en busca de su compaero, Sergio lo apunta con un arma y libera a Victoria; al escapar del yugo de los delincuentes, Victoria desea descubrir quien est detrs del rapto. Un angustiado Felipe comenta las intenciones de Nicols de rescatar a Victoria, mientras esta ltima se sorprende; Felipe defiende a Nicols, quien arriesgo su vida para salvar a Victoria. Entre tanto, en el hospital, Florencia alienta a su esposo para que despierte; Nicols abre sus ojos y lo primero que pregunta es si la polica pudo detener a los secuestradores y si su amada Victoria fue liberada.

programme.title: La Trepadora - S01:E113
programme.desc: Justo cuando Victoria le impide a Sergio anunciar su compromiso frente a la familia Guanipa, Sergio cree que la mujer se arrepintio; Victoria es quien anuncia su matrimonio, lo que sorprende a todos. Adelaida en compaa de Hansen, recuerda la niez de su hija Victoria, quien desde pequea ha sido traviesa; la sensacion de tener a su hija en peligro y no poder hacer nada desperto en ella un sentimiento ms grande. Victoria evita los besos de Sergio, quien se apresura por ponerle fecha a su matrimonio; Sergio ya ha preparado todo para casarse en una semana.

programme.title: Hollywood Weapons - S05:E03 - S-Smart Terry

programme.title: Royal Documentaries - S01:E42 - Diana A Model Princess
programme.desc: Dianas fashion sense was something people often looked at closely. She had a knack for picking outfits that were both stylish and sophisticated, which always grabbed attention. Her hats were another standout feature; she often wore elegant designs that added a touch of grace to her look. Her hair was also iconic, usually styled neatly with a slight bounce, perfectly framing her face and adding to her elegant appearance.

programme.title: Royal Documentaries - S01:E43 - Diana A Day In The Life
programme.desc: When Diana got engaged, she was constantly in the medias eyes. Throughout her life, she focused on her sons and committed herself to charity work, like speaking out against land mines. Diana used her fame to bring attention to this and other important issues. This well-researched show takes a closer look at one of the 20th centurys most amazing people. With never-before-seen footage, it shows her path from a shy teen to becoming the beloved Diana, Princess of Wales, including touching moments from her last days.
